definitions.definition: Not written clearly enough to be deciphered .
examples: a machine that cut up secret documents into small unreadable fragments

definitions.definition: Making an unpleasant reading experience, e.g. because it is dull or upsetting .
Not able to be accessed or played by some technical device.
